reviewText: After searching every where on line, this was a great find at a great price. Arrived on time and was well packaged.
Excelent! Super sellet! Great comunication and fast shipping. Thanks for all. Gracias por todo! Vendedor ms que recomendable.

Mis Favoritas is a reissue, containing the CD Oye Mi Canto Los Exitos and the DVD Evolution Tour Live In Miami. This product is manufactured by Sony Music in Colombia. Very rare, nominated for collectors and fans of the singer.
